        <li><strong>Approve with one click</strong> and they appear live on your site automatically.</li>
        <li><strong>Embed anywhere</strong> — website homepage, "about" page, pricing page, wherever couples land.</li>
      </ol>

      <h2 style="font-size:1.6rem;font-weight:700;margin-top:2.5rem;">When to ask for a testimonial</h2>
      <p>Timing is everything. The best testimonials come when emotion is highest — right after couples receive their gallery. Don't wait months. Send your collection link with the gallery delivery email: <em>"I'd love to hear how everything went. If you have a moment to share your experience, here's a quick link: [link]"</em></p>
      <p style="margin-top:1rem;">SocialProof gives you a single shareable link you can drop into any email, text, or DM. No clunky form builder. No Google Form aesthetics that don't match your brand.</p>

      <h2 style="font-size:1.6rem;font-weight:700;margin-top:2.5rem;">Display where it converts</h2>
      <p>The highest-leverage placement for wedding photographers: your pricing page. That's where couples hesitate. A rotating widget showing 5-star testimonials directly below your packages answers objections before they form.</p>
      <ul style="padding-left:1.5rem;line-height:1.9;">
        <li>Pricing page — right below your package options</li>
        <li>Homepage hero — next to your lead image</li>
        <li>About page — proof that you're as good as you claim</li>
